<Recipe name="LLM">
	<About>
		<description>
			This recipe demonstrates the usage of the LLM processor to interact with an AI language model. 
			It sends a prompt requesting a short poem about the beauty of nature, retrieves the response, and logs it. 
			The LLM processor requires an API key for authentication, which is passed securely using a system variable. 
			This example showcases how Anteater can integrate conversational AI capabilities into automated workflows, 
			enabling dynamic content generation or intelligent assistance within test and control scenarios.
		</description> 
		<author name="OpenAI GPT" email="support@openai.com" messager="ChatGPT" phone="+1-800-000-0000" /> 
		<attach>
			<file name="LLM_Usage_Guide.pdf" width="800" height="600" /> 
		</attach> 
	</About> 
	<Extern class="LLM" apiKey="$var{OPENAI_API_KEY}">
		<Prompt name="responseText">Write a short poem about the beauty of nature.</Prompt> 
		<Out name="responseText" level="info" /> 
	</Extern> 
</Recipe> 
